p'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["221"],"no-unused-vars","'Typography' is defined but never used.","Identifier","unusedVar","'Phone' is defined but never used.","'Switch' is defined but never used.","'check' is assigned a value but never used.","'setCheck' is assigned a value but never used.","'Check' is defined but never used.","'cycle' is assigned a value but never used.","React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'cb' and 'date'. Either include them or remove the dependency array. If 'cb' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["222"],"'unBlackList' is assigned a value but never used.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'cb'. Either include it or remove the dependency array. If 'cb' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["223"],"'show' is assigned a value but never used.","no-const-assign","'bl' is constant.","const","'AddBox' is defined but never used.","no-global-assign","no-unsafe-negation",{"desc":"224","fix":"225"},{"desc":"226","fix":"227"},{"desc":"228","fix":"229"},{"desc":"230","fix":"231"},{"desc":"232","fix":"233"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [loadTopMenu]",{"range":"234","text":"235"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [history, ready]",{"range":"236","text":"237"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [loadTop]",{"range":"238","text":"239"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [cb, date]",{"range":"240","text":"241"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [cb]",{"range":"242","text":"243"},[465,467],"[loadTopMenu]",[1131,1133],"[history, ready]",[1163,1165],"[loadTop]",[1666,1668],"[cb, date]",[1177,1179],"[cb]"]